Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:02.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:05.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was forced to take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:08.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the organization learned that Shin'ichi and Conan were the same person,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.39,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}everyone close to me would be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:12.62,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only one who knows the truth is Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:15.43,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hide my identity yet again today, in which there is only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing\Nas "the perfect crime".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to say this, but your\Ncrime is as clear as daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've made three very basic mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistake #1: Cans scattered around\Nthe waste bin in an unnatural fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number of cans is proof enough\Nthat there's something inside the bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistake #2: The ice cream bar you\Nwere just eating is lying nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. You were in a rush to hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you dropped it on the ground, half-eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistake #3: The most\Nincriminating evidence of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is that I can see your big butt\Ninside the waste bin, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You talk too much, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! I found Genta too! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:38.12,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:43.32,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's no fun when you're "it"â€”\Nthe game always ends right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:45.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's no fun for me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:49.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A high school student playing\Ndetective games in the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These badges are so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Detective Boys!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:03:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the only primary school students\Nin the world with badges like these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:05.28,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There are tiny transceivers built inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.98,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can communicate over long distances
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.12,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}by using the dial on the back to change frequencies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:14.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's perfect for kids' games,\Nbut I'd rather not have to play myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If they hadn't come over\Nto invite me to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:19.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I would've gone with Ran to\NTeitan University's school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:26.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't you worry! I'll have plenty\Nof fun with the university girls for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok! This time I'll be the detective\Nand you guys'll be the criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to be a criminal again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We only need one detective!\NNow get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:42.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love Hide-and-Seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't believe I keep\Ngoing along with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What happens if this keeps up\Nand I turn stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:57.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Upsy daisy. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,99, 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here I come! Time to show you all\Nthe skill of Genta Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,leader of the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta's looking hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Multiple girls kidnapped and murdered."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They haven't caught them yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cute girls are the only ones\Nthey're going after.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means I'm in huge danger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something bad ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you'd be there to protect me,\Nwouldn't you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we're destined\Nto be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on now, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found you, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may be good at finding people,\Nbut you sure suck at hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate running away\Nand hiding from people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird though, I could\Nswear I heard Ayumi's voice too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Stupid! Hurry and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Somewhere for me to hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's keepin' that moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odd. Scientifically speaking,\Nhe shouldn't have found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was scientific about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! That leaves just Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That dumb Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long can it possibly take him\Nto find an ordinary little girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is {\i1}not{\i0} an ordinary little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:12.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Guess l'll tune up the skateboard\Nthe Doc gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, do you mind if I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you... How do you\Nfeel about Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you how you\Nfeel about her as a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As just a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko... Don't tell me you\Nhave a crush on Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! I'm simply asking your opinion\Nto help me decide on my "life plan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Life plan? You're not talking\Nabout marriage, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky! The Doctor\Nmakes so much stuff for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gimme a break! Kids these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What took you so damn long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! I already said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble if we don't get movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}still{\i0} haven't found Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just give up and have her come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I'd ever say anything\Nthat uncool in front of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:25.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah! So Genta likes Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10} too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:29.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After all, we're destined\Nto be together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a situation\NI've gotten myself into...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's call it quits.\NYou can come out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think she went\Nhome without us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe something happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:51.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll turn the volume up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.19,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.61,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NSomewhere dark and cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:14.09,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How did I get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.19,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hid in the trunk of a car\Nthat was stopped in front of the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.96,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But then I got sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In front of the park?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:29.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:34.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Money! There's tons\Nof it in a paper bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A million yen times 100, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hundred million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car must belong to someone rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:48.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why would that much money be in a paper bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.36,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is there anything else\Nbesides the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is. It looks\Nlike a plastic bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it filled with grilled eel lunches?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, look, a saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A saw...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's this thing?\NIt's slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. You been hearin'\Na kid's voice come from the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off. There's no way\Nthat thing could talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.75,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is the saw the only thing\Ninside the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's also something round\Nand wrapped in paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.46,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let me see what's inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't open that, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a head! A girl's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A girl's head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me the car Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10} got in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}belonged to those kidnappers\Nwho're killing little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Something's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me check out the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, unlock it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! So that's what we heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That had me scared for a minute there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.95,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't cry!{fix time}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!\NThey'll hear you if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.75,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I know! Think of something funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just remembered how\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} looked like a bear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he fell down the stairs\Nthe other day and got two bumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}. You can stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:52.21,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Be quiet and don't move a muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how are you gonna chase them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're in a car, you know!\NIt'll be hopeless with that skateboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Doc made this for me.\NIt's no ordinary skateboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's equipped with a\Nhigh-performance turbo engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:22.71,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But it's solar powered, so you can\Nonly use it when the sun is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:26.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One hour until sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?\NYou guys wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car belongs to\Na couple of murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder, schmurder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit here\Nwhile Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Protecting women is a man's duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Where's the car now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car's weird, it keeps\Nmoving and then stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus there are weird sounds outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn up your badge's volume, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! They're stuck in traffic\Nbecause of road construction!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:07.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only place around here\Nwhere there's construction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}is at the intersection on 2nd Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We can still catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Better hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:25.04,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no reason to kill her, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her parents paid the ransom,\Nand besides, she's just a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool! She's seen our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't leave her alive!\NEven if she is just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:41.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hang on, Ayumi! We're coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where's their car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi! Are you still stopping and going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But it's not\Nthe same place as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't hear those\Nweird sounds anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,plus the car just drove a long way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.38,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}plus the car just drove a long way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:08.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on. If they're in a\Ntraffic jam up ahead, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! The highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:14.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad! There's no catching them\Nif they get on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There sure have been a lot\Nof police cars passing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the fourth one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:26.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is something going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.64,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...the kidnappers appear to have\Nescaped to Beika Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.17,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The authorities have\Nformed a police cordon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:37.61,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and are trying as hard\Nas possible to arrest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Have you\Nheard any police cars?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:44.65,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah! About 3 of them passed\Nby when we were stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it!\NThey've set up an inspection checkpoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably where the roads converge\Nright before the highway starts:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on Beika Bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Beika Bridge is straight\Ndown that last street!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. They wouldn't dare\Ngo through the checkpoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd obviously take a side street to get out of Beika without going over the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:17.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They'll have to come down this street!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.72,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're moving! The car's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bring it on! You're as good as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are they?\NIt's already been 5 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What the heck's going on, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Is the car stopped\Nright now? Or is it moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say something, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did she go out of range?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:47.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, these things have a\Nbroadcast radius of 20 kilometres!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no way they could've\Ngone that far in 5 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's in a tunnel\Nor something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Tunnel! That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, they'd have to pass through the\Ninspection point and go over the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to enter Beika Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means they must be inside a\Nbuilding that disrupts our signals!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't think it's\Ntheir hideout, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nthey're like rats in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police'll find them eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll find Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}\Nbefore they get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.51,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's seen our faces.\NWe can't leave her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:20.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even if she is just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If something bad ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}you'd be there to protect me,\Nwouldn't you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.99,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...na... {\i1}ku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.49,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't you say anything, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Calm down, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.63,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They'll hear you if you yell too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.27,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no way they would hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:46.14,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The car's so loud that\NI can't hear their voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where you are right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! There was this roaring sound\Nand then you stopped replying to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:56.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Roaring sound? So they {\i1}were{\i0} in the tunnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:59.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But how did they pass\Nthrough the checkpoint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll come after you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just keep quiet and wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The skateboard'll stop\Nsoon if we don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:28.18,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}! It sounds like the car's\Nin some sort of shop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard someone say, "Welcome",\Nand this weird sound just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A gas station! Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:40.96,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}! Let me hear\Nwhat's going on outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're currently giving away Yaiba towels and T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.53,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We don't need any!\NWe're in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only gas station where you can get Kamen Yaiba goods
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is Yotsubishi Gas,\Nwhich we just passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10}'s definitely\Nin the trunk of that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As is the girl's head and the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:27.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They're the ones kidnapping and killing little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear\Nanything strange just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just some kids playing pranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:51.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}! Respond! Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, something's definitely strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably just a stray cat.\NNo need to get worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bastards! There's no escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! There's not enough solar power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:13.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We have to do something\Nbefore we stop altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop, you kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop the car! Or else I'll do {\i1}this{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who were those kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hell if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just hurry! There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ugh! My hands are going numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:08.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't hold on any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi! Ayumi! Ayumi! Ayumi! Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares?! Let's just get her\Nout of there and split!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:37.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had us worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who've been kidnapping\Nand murdering little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murdering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no point in playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard your guys'\Nconversation in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You said you'd have no trouble killing little kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then there's the corpse and money in your trunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try talking your way out of that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a better look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all hand-made props!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Props?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our conversation in the car was us\Npracticing our lines one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Practicing your lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:45.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Teitan University School Festival"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're performing in a play here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's go to Teitan University's\Nschool festival, Conan{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:54.58,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hear they're going to have\Nan interesting mystery play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides, they said on the radio\Nthat they just caught the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So was that the real killer then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been smashed and the head's busted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was nice meeting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to take\Nresponsibility for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.87,0:23:05.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"We Won't Live to See Tomorrow"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her parents paid the r... ransom,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and besides, she's just a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool! She's seen our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't leave her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's something weird\Nabout that actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't stand up straight,\Nand he keeps blowing his lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so beautiful, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do tea, let's do tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, now! Wouldn't you like to see my famous detective skillsâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta! Say the next line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:44.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to read this word!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:47.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's rightâ€”we were put onstage as a main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:47.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's pronounced "cruel"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:51.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:51.12,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Incidentally, the role of the decapitated head...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:53.69,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...went to Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-chan{\r\be10} herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.69,0:23:56.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hate Hide-and-Seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she just found her father, too! How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still no saying for sure\Nthat he was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:17.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on! Make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.97,0:24:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? What's happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.96,0:24:30.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.97,0:24:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: A Hundred Million Yen
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.97,0:24:35.97,Signs,,0,0,0,,A hundred million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:38.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time too, the puzzle is big!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:05.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
